       Change Summary Explanation
       FY 2025 budget request decreased by $0.700 million due to Small Business Innovation Research/Small Business Technology Transfer (SBIR/STTR).

       FY 2026 funding request increased by a total of $30.891 million due to an increase of $30.900 million for Reconciliation funding incongruence and a $0.009
       million decrease for Small Business Innovation Research/Small Business Technology Transfer (SBIR/STTR).

       The FY 2026 President's Budget submittal did not reflect the FY 2027 through FY 2030 funding. Therefore, an explanation of the changes between the two
       budget positions for FY 2027 cannot be made in a relevant manner.

