 mobilization authorizations, and automates and synchronizes the ARC utilization process to rapidly generate capability, increase lethality, and enable predictive analytics
 and data-driven decision making. The Air Force cannot execute the Secretary of Defense's national security priorities without mobilizing the forces and capabilities in the
