under the GPS Navigation Warfare (NAVWAR) Research, Development, Test, and Evaluation (RDT&E) Memorandum of
Understanding (MOU) to develop resilient and assured Positioning, Navigation and Timing (PNT) technologies to reduce Pulse
Per Second (PPS) receiver development cost.
