elements. In parallel, ION will define the acquisition strategy for FY26-FY27 supporting emerging mission requirements and utilize the most practical vehicle(s) and
methods available within Federal Acquisition Regulation (FAR) and non-FAR contracts, agreements and solicitation methods.

