of Government Reference Architectures. Keeping pace with and getting ahead of adversary advances is a critical component of
our Offensive Space Control Force Design analysis. Specifying Space Force Design (offense and defense) is only the start of our
SSDP responsibilities. The program will also be focused on Enhancing Space Control Weapon Effectiveness; requiring SSDP
to collaborate with our stakeholders to ensure system readiness and effectivity. Finally, understanding the impact of space to
the cross-domain fight for both the US and our adversaries is an increasingly important aspect of SSDP's Space and the Cross-
